column2: Golar LNG Partners LP engages in the logistics solutions. The firm operates through the LNG market segment. The firm's fleet consists of approximately six FSRUs and over four LNG carriers. The firm's FSRU vessels include Golar Spirit, Golar Winter, Golar Freeze, NR Satu, Golar Igloo and Golar Eskimo. Its FSRU vessels have a total capacity of approximately 846,000 cubic meters. The firm's LNG carriers include Golar Mazo, Methane Princess, Golar Grand and Golar Maria. Its LNG carriers have a total capacity of over 564,400 cubic meters.
